OL,3,C'Disgraceful': Mum dies from cancer
OL,4,Csix days after misdiagnosis
OL,6,FThe families of two people who died
OL,7,Fafter their cancer symptoms were
OL,8,Fmissed by the same hospital trust have
OL,9,Fbranded the situation "disgraceful".
OL,11,FThe families, both from , are calling
OL,12,Ffor urgent improvements to diagnosis
OL,13,Fprocedures at United Lincolnshire
OL,14,FHospitals NHS Trust.
OL,16,FMartin Hilton's mother, Janet, was a
OL,17,Ffull-time carer for her husband, Ken,
OL,18,Fwho has Parkinson's disease.
