OL,6,FBut in January 2021 she started
OL,7,Fexperiencing pain and swelling in her
OL,8,Fabdomen.
OL,10,FShe was taken to accident and
OL,11,Femergency, but doctors at Boston
OL,12,FPilgrim Hospital discharged her after
OL,13,F12 hours because they were unable to
OL,14,Fidentify the problem.
OL,16,FTwo weeks later she was told she had
OL,17,Fincurable liver cancer and moved to a
OL,18,Fhospice, where she died six days later.
