OL,6,FMr Hilton said: "She was the best mum
OL,7,Fever. She had the biggest heart, she
OL,8,Fwould do anything for anyone.
OL,10,F"She was the most wonderful person."
OL,12,FHe added: "I think it was disgusting,
OL,13,FI think it's disgraceful. Mum had gone
OL,14,Ftwo weeks prior and (they said)
OL,15,F'absolutely nothing wrong with you, go
OL,16,Fhome'.
OL,18,F"She was sat there at two o'clock in
OL,19,Fthe morning and told 'you've got
OL,20,Fincurable liver cancer'.
