OL,6,F"On her own, at 78-years-old, what
OL,7,Fmust have been going through poor
OL,8,Fmum's mind?"
OL,10,FTwo nurses who work for the same
OL,11,Fhospital trust say their relative was
OL,12,Falso failed.
OL,14,FThey asked to remain anonymous to
OL,15,Fprotect their jobs.
OL,17,FOne told ITV News: "He contacted his
OL,18,FGP with pain in his ribs. They told
OL,19,Fhim it was a cracked rib and they
OL,20,Fdon't treat that.
