OL,6,F"He went back multiple times (but)
OL,7,Fthey didn't take into account that
OL,8,Fhe'd lost 20kg.
OL,10,F"He waited ten weeks for a scan,
OL,11,Furgent care saw him, eventually he had
OL,12,Fan emergency admission and he was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with stage four cancer."
OL,15,FThe other nurse said she wanted to
OL,16,Fspeak out because "patients are dying
OL,17,Fwhen they don't need to".
