OL,6,F"Something needs to change and it's
OL,7,Fvery frustrating as a nurse seeing
OL,8,Fthis and now having experienced that
OL,9,Fwith a loved one, and it's still
OL,10,Fhappening," she said.
OL,12,FThe families contacted ITV News after
OL,13,Fwe reported on the
OL,15,FUnited Lincolnshire Hospitals NHS
OL,16,FTrust said it could not comment on
OL,17,Findividual cases.
